foods.description: TURTLE SUNDAE PUDDING SNACKS, TURTLE SUNDAE
foods.lowercaseDescription: turtle sundae pudding snacks, turtle sundae
foods.ingredients: PUDDING BASE INGREDIENTS: SKIM MILK, WATER, SUGAR, MODIFIED CORNSTARCH, CREAM, CONTAINS LESS THAN 2% OF SALT, CALCIUM PHOSPHATE, SODIUM STEAROYL LACTYLATE, SODIUM ALGINATE, CAROB BEAN GUM, NATURAL AND ARTIFICIAL FLAVOR, VITAMIN A PALMITATE, VITAMIN D3, TITANIUM DIOXIDE (COLOR), CARAMEL COLOR, YELLOW 6. TOPPING INGREDIENTS: SUGAR, ALMONDS, PECANS, VEGETABLE OIL BLEND (PALM AND PALM KERNEL OILS), COCOA (PROCESSED WITH ALKALI), CONTAINS LESS THAN 2% OF WHOLE MILK POWDER, SOY LECITHIN, NATURAL FLAVOR, SALT.

WHITE CHOCOLATE (SUGAR, COCOA BUTTER, DRY WHOLE MILK, SOY LECITHIN [AN EMULSIFIER], VANILLA EXTRACT), COOKIE (SUGAR, ENRICHED WHEAT FLOUR [WHEAT FLOUR, NIACIN, REDUCED IRON, THIAMINE MONONITRATE {VITAMIN B1}, RIBOFLAVIN {VITAMIN B2}, FOLIC ACID], PALM OIL, CANOLA OIL, HIGH FRUCTOSE CORN SYRUP, SALT, BAKING SODA, CINNAMON, SOY LECITHIN [AN EMULSIFIER], ARTIFICIAL FLAVOR, NATURAL FLAVOR), ORANGE DRIZZLE (SUGAR, VEGETABLE OIL [PALM KERNEL OIL, HYDROGENATED PALM KERNEL OIL], MILK SOLIDS, WHEY POWDER, NONFAT MILK SOLIDS, ARTIFICIAL COLOR [FD&C YELLOW #6], SOY LECITHIN [AN EMULSIFIER], SALT, ARTIFICIAL FLAVOR), NONPAREILS (SUGAR, DEXTRIN, TAPIOCA STARCH, CARNAUBA WAX, MAGNESIUM SILICATE, GLYCERIN, GUM ARABIC, GLUCOSE, GLUCOSE POWDER, FD&C YELLOW #6, FD&C YELLOW #5, FD&C RED #40), GOLD SANDING SUGAR (SUGAR, CARNAUBA WAX, FD&C YELLOW #5, FD&C YELLOW #6, FD&C BLUE #2, FD&C RED #40, CONFECTIONER'S GLAZE).
